name: Skin Diamond
description:
Skin Diamond

This is another TI off my list ;)

I trained her for 10,000 steps and found the 3k-5k range looks the best to me. This upload represents the 5000 step version. I used 45 pictures, quite easy to find if you know where to look,

I used the base v1.5 SD model for training, but highly recommend using any of the top rated checkpoints here.

PLEASE send along any tips and advice you have, I want to make this model as good and foolproof as possible, thanks!

NOTE: Not gonna lie, this was difficult to pull off because (1) most of the very best and most life like gens were nsfw. (Don't know why that would happen) and (2) because of her heritage (her father is Eritrean) the tendency is for her for to come out looking more Asian than African. I'm going to keep working and update when possible.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
